class Prod {
    constructor(props){
        this.name = props.name
        this.price = props.price
        this.img = props.img
        this.hover = props.hover
        this.slider = [...props.slider]
        this.view = props.view
        this.desc = props.desc
    }
}

const allProducts = [
    new Prod({
        name: 'Aform Barstool',
        price: 350.00,
        img: "https://demo.quemalabs.com/ocin-lite/wp-content/uploads/2016/01/product1.jpg",
        hover: "https://demo.quemalabs.com/ocin-lite/wp-content/uploads/2016/01/product1_2.jpg",
        slider: ["https://demo.quemalabs.com/ocin-lite/wp-content/uploads/2016/01/product1.jpg",
        "https://demo.quemalabs.com/ocin-lite/wp-content/uploads/2016/01/product1_2.jpg", 
        "https://demo.quemalabs.com/ocin-lite/wp-content/uploads/2016/01/602780_Form_Barstool_65cm_WhiteOak_3.jpeg"],
        view: 'banner',
        desc: {
            material: "Shell, Plastic",
            legs: "Oak",
            size: "77cm",
            seat_H: "65cm",
            prod_info: "Made by order. Production time: 8-10 weeks",
            delivery: "Street level only"
        }
    }),
    
    new Prod({
        name: 'Astro Tray',
        price: 79,
        img: "https://demo.quemalabs.com/ocin-lite/wp-content/uploads/2016/01/3569_Astro_Tray_All_1.jpeg",
        hover: "https://demo.quemalabs.com/ocin-lite/wp-content/uploads/2016/01/356995_Astro_Tray_32x20_1.jpeg",
        slider: ["https://demo.quemalabs.com/ocin-lite/wp-content/uploads/2016/01/3569_Astro_Tray_All_1.jpeg",
        "https://demo.quemalabs.com/ocin-lite/wp-content/uploads/2016/01/356995_Astro_Tray_32x20_1.jpeg",
        "https://demo.quemalabs.com/ocin-lite/wp-content/uploads/2016/01/356995_Astro_Tray_32x20_2.jpeg"],
        view: 'standart',
        desc: {
            material: "Oak",
            length: "32cm",
            depth: "20cm",
            height: "2cm",
            prod_info: "Approved for food. Clean with damp cloth"
        }
    })
]


export default allProducts
